Reasoning: The paper deals with the analysis of a corpus of quotations in the Russian Wiktionary, which involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques such as parsing and database design. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) or Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of a machine-readable dictionary and the building of a histogram of distribution of quotations suggest that the paper could also belong to the Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), or Databases (cs.DB) sub-categories.
